<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idf67cd0c6-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5" identifier="/us/usc/t46/s7319"><num value="7319">§ 7319.</num><heading> Records of merchant mariners’ documents</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary shall maintain records on each merchant mariner’s document issued, including the name and address of the individual to whom issued and the next of kin of the individual.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idf67cd0c7-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5">(<ref href="/us/pl/98/89">Pub. L. 98–89</ref>, <date date="1983-08-26">Aug. 26, 1983</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/97/545">97 Stat. 545</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/108/293/tIV/s403">Pub. L. 108–293, title IV, § 403</ref>, <date date="2004-08-09">Aug. 9, 2004</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/118/1043">118 Stat. 1043</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/116/283/dG/tLVXXXV">Pub. L. 116–283, div. G, title LVXXXV</ref> [LXXXV], § 8505(b)(4), <date date="2021-01-01">Jan. 1, 2021</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/134/4751">134 Stat. 4751</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
